Application Developer - Java
Department :  Commercial (BP15880)

Job Overview
Company is known for our pioneering technologies and products within the commercial automotive industry. We are providing development framework and components to serve DSIT and ISUZU at IT delivery area.

Responsibilities and Duties

Develop and maintain internal libraries, components, and tools, with the technology stack of .NET, Java, and front-end frameworks.
Responsible for problem-resolving internal cases related to the development technologies.
Responsible for composing development-related articles and publicizing them in the internal community.
Passionate about providing technical guidance to others and providing them with technical solutions.

Qualification & Skills

 Good English communication skills.
Strong analytical & problem-solving skills.
Strong mindset on teamwork.
Mandatory Skills

More than one year of experience in software development, and solid knowledge of Java, Spring, Sprint Boot, and Web services.
Familiar with Maven/Gradle and other build tools.
Proficient in web front-end development technologies like HTML5, CSS, and JavaScript.
Familiar with RDBMS.Good knowledge and mindset of OOP.
Desirable Technical Skills, but not mandatory

Familiar with .NET development.
Familiar with modern front-end frameworks like Angular, React, Vue, etc.
Know some NoSQL databases.
Good knowledge and mindset of FP.
DevOps experience will be an advantage.
Experience of Agile WOW.
